<div class="container body-container">
    <h3 class="text-center">Donut delivery so excelent it could only be from space</h3>
    
    <div id="carouselExampleSlidesOnly" class="carousel slide carousel-image text-center navbar-shadow" data-ride="carousel" data-interval="3000">
        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
        </ol>
        <div class="carousel-inner carousel-outline darken" role="listbox">
            <div class="carousel-item item active">
                <%= image_tag("Donut-Wallpaper-1.jpg", alt: "First Slide", :class => "d-block carousel-image img-fluid darken") %>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item item">
                <%= image_tag("Donut-Wallpaper-2.jpg", alt: "First Slide", :class => "d-block carousel-image img-fluid darken") %>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item item">
                <%= image_tag("Donut-Wallpaper-3.jpg", alt: "First Slide", :class => "d-block carousel-image img-fluid darken") %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="divider-new fade-in">
        <h2>Our Promise</h2>
    </div>
    <section id="our-promise" class="text-center fade-in">
        <p>Our donuts will be delivered fresh to your door within 2 hours. We take pride
        in our average customer satisfaction rating of 246% and hope to improve with
        your order. Space n' Glaze is a dedicated business that really cares and will
        do everything to make your donut delivery the best possible.</p>
    </section>
    
    <div class="divider-new fade-in">
        <h2>Customer Testimonials</h2>
    </div>
    <section id="testimonials">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-1">
                <p class="fade-in">"These donuts are so good they fixed my marriage! Thanks
                Space n' Glaze!" -Yim Oudom</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-2">
                <p class="fade-in">"I have honestly never had a better donut, especially not
                one that is delivered to my house. I got evicted from my house
                for not paying rent because I spent all my money on donuts,
                so now I can't really utilize the delivery service, but I still
                love this place" -Mak Sov</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <%= link_to "Place an Order", '#', class: 'btn btn-lg btn-success btn-block font-text navbar-shadow outline fade-in' %>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <%= link_to "Contact Us", new_contact_path, class: 'btn btn-lg btn-primary btn-block font-text navbar-shadow outline fade-in' %>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="spacing"></div>
    <footer class="footer navbar-toggleable-md navbar-shadow outline navbar-bottom">
      <h3 class="text-center">Sam Williams: <%= link_to "Github", 'https://github.com/PaperXLV/', target: :_blank %>, Sam@ukethat.com</h3>
    </footer>
</div>